    Frequently Asked Questions

    Will this work where prescription antifungals failed?

    Yes. Many people find success with tea tree oil's natural antifungal properties after synthetic medications stopped working or caused side effects. Our soap penetrates deeper than most creams.

    How is this different from the creams and sprays I've tried?

    Most treatments only work on the surface. Our soap penetrates deep into skin layers where fungus hides, killing it completely rather than just suppressing symptoms.

    Can I use this every day without irritation?

    Absolutely. Unlike harsh prescription treatments, our natural formula is gentle enough for daily use while being powerful enough to kill stubborn fungal infections.

    What are the main benefits for chronic athlete's foot?

    • Kills fungus completely, not just symptoms
    • Prevents embarrassing relapses and reinfections
    • Eliminates foot odor at the source
    • Restores confidence to go barefoot anywhere
    • Works where other treatments have failed

    How long until I can wear sandals without shame?

    Most people notice reduced itching and odor within 1-2 weeks. For completely clear, confident feet suitable for sandals and going barefoot, 4-6 weeks of consistent use works best.

    Will this prevent it from coming back like it always does?

    Yes! The key is using it consistently for the full treatment period to kill fungus completely. Many people stop too early when symptoms disappear, allowing reinfection.

    Can I use this if I have very sensitive or cracked skin?

    Yes. Our formula soothes while it heals. The aloe vera and coconut oil calm irritated skin while the tea tree oil kills the infection causing the damage.

    Will this work on toenail fungus too?

    While primarily designed for athlete's foot, many customers report improvement in nail fungus when used consistently. The antifungal properties can help prevent nail infections from spreading.
